import Finished from "./TextEditor"
import {
  BrowserRouter,
  Routes,
  Route,
  Navigate,
} from "react-router-dom"
import { v4 as uuidV4 } from "uuid"

function App() {
  
  return (
    <BrowserRouter>
      <Routes>
        <Route path="/" exact>
          <Navigate element={`/documents/${uuidV4()}`} />
        </Route>
        <Route path="/documents/:id">
          <TextEditor />
        </Route>
      </Routes>
    </BrowserRouter>
  )
}

export default App
